{
  "stem": "18572.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 367.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I think she didn't even talk to him because he wasn't coming with us or he was making her go.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I said goodbye to my father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That was it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This must have been October of '42--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--because that's when the ghetto was liquidated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went to this man to-- who was gonna hide us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we learned that the very next day, the ghetto was liquidated.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he must have known, and that's why he came and insisted that we leave that day.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was some sort of false wall and some sort of a hiding space that we were hidden in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't have very strong memories of this place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know that this man who was supposed to keep us for the duration did not keep us for very long.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother has told me it wasn't very long.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't have such strong feelings of this place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the next place that we went to--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--I remember we were walking along a road, and I was very tired.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember sitting down and saying, I'm not going anymore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- you know, I just-- I want to walk.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother picked out this house, this farmhouse, and apparently knocked on the door.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they took us in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were religious people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were some sort of evangelical sect.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they took us in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were very poor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They hid us in the barn, where they dug out a hole, on top of which a pig stood.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The hole was long enough that my mother and I could lie down, just, you know-- like, if one of us was in the back, the other one had to be on the side.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We could not stand up.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
